Template: pisugar-server/address
Type: select
Choices: 0.0.0.0, 127.0.0.1
Default: 0.0.0.0
Description: PiSugar server listening address (choose 127.0.0.1 to prohibit public access).

Template: pisugar-server/web
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: enable/disable http server on port 8421, and websocket on port 8422.

Template: pisugar-server/tcp
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: enable/disable tcp server on port 8423.

Template: pisugar-server/uds
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: enable/disable uds server on /tmp/pisugar-server.sock.
